aparam api tadabhāve dūṣaṇam āha. asaṃprajanyam eva saṃprajanyābhāvaḥ kleśasvabhāvaś cauraḥ, kuśaladhanāpaharaṇāt. tena smṛtimoṣānusāriṇā rakṣapālabhūtāyāḥ smṛteḥ pramoṣam abhāvam anusṛtya muṣitā viluptakuśaladhanāḥ santaḥ upacityāpi puṇyāni kuśaladhanānāṃ saṃcayaṃ kṛtvāpi durgatiparāyaṇā bhavanti.

<commentary>kutaḥ punar evam ity uktam evārthaṃ spaṣṭayann āha.

taskarāś caurāḥ, teṣāṃ saṃghāto avatāragaveṣakaḥ piśācavad avatāramārgaprekṣī, chidrānveṣaṇatatpara ityarthaḥ. prāpyāvatāraṃ praveśamārgam āsādya muṣṇāti. tato hanti śobhanagataye jīvitapratilambhaṃ kuśalapātheyābhāvāt.</commentary>

smṛtim adhikṛtyādhunā prāha. yataḥ smṛter abhāve dūṣaṇam evaṃ syāt. tasmād idam atra doṣaṃ paśyatā smṛtir ālabambhanāsaṃpramoṣalakṣaṇā manodvārān manogṛhapraveśamārgāt nāpaneyā nāpasāryā, sadāvasthāpayitavyety arthaḥ.
